&lt;img src="img/rules/no_drone_zoneFAA.PNG" width=70%&gt;



Airspace restrictions


    &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li class="fragment"&gt;Security Sensitive Airspace Restrictions&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li class="fragment"&gt;Temporary Flight Restrictions (TFRs)&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li class="fragment"&gt;Restricted or Special Use Airspace&lt;/li&gt;
